"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"Athena Strates ist eine südafrikanische Schauspielerin (* 12. November 1996), bekannt aus den Filmen „Genius: Picasso“, „The Good Liar“, „A Perfect Enemy“, „Aufbruch ins Ungewisse“ und „Die Nachtschwestern“.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Athena Strates is a South African (on November 12 1996) actress known for Genius: Picasso, The Good Liar, A Perfect Enemy, Aufbruch ins Ungewisse and Die Nachtschwestern.","name":"Athena Strates","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CH","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"Athena Strates","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Афина Стрэйтс","primary":false}}]}},"person_574378_translations":{"at":1772689464883,"data":{"id":574378,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Amber Rose Revah (born June 24, 1986) is an English born actress.\n\nShe played Hala Hussein, Saddam Hussein's daughter, in the BBC/HBO series House of Saddam. Later she appeared in From Paris With Love (2010) and Aazaan (2011).  She also acted in Son Of God and The Bible series. Revah made several appearances in other smaller acting roles.","name":"Amber Rose Revah","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"GR","iso_639_1":"el","name":"ελληνικά","english_name":"Greek","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IR","iso_639_1":"fa","name":"فارسی","english_name":"Persian","data":{"biography":"","name":"امبر رز روا","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Ембер Роуз Рева","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Эмбер Роуз Рева","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IL","iso_639_1":"he","name":"עִבְרִית","english_name":"Hebrew","data":{"biography":"","name":"אמבר רוז ריווה","primary":false}}]}},"person_1678286_translations":{"at":1772689474575,"data":{"id":1678286,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"段博文，中国新生代演员。2006年因主演第5代摄影大师吕乐导演作品《十三棵泡桐》踏入影视圈。主要代表作有：《秘岸》《万有引力》《观音山》《有种》等优秀影视作品。在电影《十三棵泡桐树》中，段博文通过“陶陶”一角充分的诠释了一个青春期的男生成长的冲动、孤独、困惑和迷茫，被导演笑着赞为“灵气小生”。 段博文在张元导演的电影《有种》里面，饰演一个不愿意说话的“哑巴”男孩，单纯靠眼神的表演，对他的演技更是一个新挑战。从坏学生，到混混，到痴情男，再到哑巴，段博文的表演值得期待。","name":"段博文","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Duan Bowen","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"Duan Bowen","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"段博文，中國新生代演員。2006 年因主演第 5 代攝影大師呂樂導演作品《十三棵泡桐》踏入影視圈。主要代表作有：《秘岸》《萬有引力》《觀音山》《有種》等優秀影視作品。在電影《十三棵泡桐樹》中，段博文透過 透過 通過“陶陶”一角充分的詮釋了一個青春期的男生成長的衝動、孤獨、困惑和迷茫，被導演笑著贊為“靈氣小生”。\n\n段博文在張元導演的電影《有種》裏面，飾演一個不願意説話的“啞巴”男孩，單純靠眼神的表演，對他的演技更是一個新挑戰。從壞學生，到混混，到痴情男，再到啞巴，段博文的表演值得期待。","name":"段博文","primary":false}}]}},"movie_7392_detail_vi-VN":{"at":1772689476362,"data":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/e6Dl1F3uPc2YoW3EZDCXKK1cAdo.jpg","belongs_to_collection":{"id":123249,"name":"Ilsa, She Wolf of the SS Collection","poster_path":"/83r8YbGHBwBk5XYULgcuznouaiU.jpg","backdrop_path":"/o03hf2Kgfx72sgYRCgGlzFiocR1.jpg"},"budget":0,"genres":[{"id":28,"name":"Phim Hành Động"},{"id":27,"name":"Phim Kinh Dị"},{"id":10752,"name":"Phim Chiến Tranh"},{"id":53,"name":"Phim Gây Cấn"}],"homepage":"","id":7392,"imdb_id":"tt0074670","origin_country":["CA","US"],"original_language":"en","original_title":"Ilsa: Harem Keeper of the Oil Sheiks","overview":"Ilsa đã trở lại! ...Mạnh mẽ hơn bao giờ hết! Với cơn thịnh nộ tàn bạo, nàng đã chinh phục cả một đế chế và gây chấn động thế giới!","popularity":0.799,"poster_path":"/4VJCCR8pHotBu1hn62vpeSsii3S.jpg","production_companies":[{"id":13032,"logo_path":null,"name":"Mount Everest Enterprises Ltd","origin_country":""}],"production_countries":[{"iso_3166_1":"CA","name":"Canada"}],"release_date":"1976-02-29","revenue":0,"runtime":94,"spoken_languages":[{"english_name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English"}],"status":"Released","tagline":"","title":"Quản lý hậu cung của trùm dầu mỏ","video":false,"vote_average":4.681,"vote_count":83}},"person_1851892_translations":{"at":1772689478066,"data":{"id":1851892,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"John J. Shim","primary":true}}]}},"person_5694532_translations":{"at":1772689478937,"data":{"id":5694532,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Masaaki Kokubo","primary":true}}]}},"person_4692742_translations":{"at":1772689483407,"data":{"id":4692742,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"River Van Coleman Crow","primary":true}}]}},"person_2823870_translations":{"at":1772691620000,"data":{"id":2823870,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Wang Yijun","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"王一钧","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"王一鈞","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"王一鈞","primary":false}}]}},"person_233590_translations":{"at":1772691620155,"data":{"id":233590,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"Yoshitsugu Matsuoka est un seiyū (doubleur) japonais.","name":"Yoshitsugu Matsuoka","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Yoshitsugu Matsuoka is a Japanese voice actor from Hokkaido. He is affiliated with I'm Enterprise. He was honored at the 6th Seiyu Awards for Best New Actor in 2012 and the 10th Seiyu Awards for Best Lead Actor in 2016. He is best known for being the voice of Kirito from Sword Art Online, Sorata Kanda from The Pet Girl of Sakurasou, Sora from No Game No Life, Arata Kasuga/Astral Trinity from Trinity Seven, Sōma Yukihira from Food Wars!: Shokugeki no Soma, and Masamune Izumi from Eromanga Sensei. As of June 17, 2019, he is the current official Guinness World Record holder for the most unique sound bites provided by a voice actor at an exceeded 10,000 words in Danmachi - Memoria Freese.","name":"Yoshitsugu Matsuoka","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"松冈祯丞（日语：松岡 禎丞／まつおか よしつぐ Matsuoka Yoshitsugu，1986年9月17日—）是一名日本男性声优，北海道出身，目前隶属于I'm Enterprise事务所。\n\n松冈祯丞出生于北海道十胜综合振兴局带广市，小学二年级搬家到附近的池田町。因为家附近地广人稀，当时网络也不发达，松冈童年有空会和朋友一起在郊外探险、抓独角仙之类充满自然感的生活。除此之外，松冈小学时期已经有订阅汽车杂志，同时受《头文字D》等动画熏陶，直到高中三年生之前仍然立志要成为汽车检修员。然而他在15岁的时候，于朋友推荐下观看了动画《新世纪福音战士》，并被动画中为渚薰配音的石田彰之演技所震惊，自此对声优这个职业产生了兴趣。松冈高中时本来在修读汽车修理相关的科系，但到高中三年级时希望挑战一下人生，于是在自学一番后进了北海道的声优学校体验一段时间。松冈后来被告知“不去东京的话很难成为专业声优”，于是决意上京，高中毕业后透过新闻奖学生制度加入了日本播音演技研究所。父亲最初反对松冈上京，但最后在“22岁前不能当上声优就要放弃”和“不会给你任何援助”的两个条件下让步。在上京初期，松冈因为没有钱的关系而需要过着半工读的宿舍生活，直到2009年才通过甄选加入I'm Enterprise事务所，当时刚好是22岁。同年，正式以《东之伊甸》“AKX20000”一役出道。","name":"松冈祯丞","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"松岡禎丞","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"É um dublador japonês de Hokkaido. Ele é afiliado à I'm Enterprise. Ele foi homenageado no 6º Seiyu Awards de Melhor Ator Novo em 2012 e no 10º Seiyu Awards de Melhor Ator Principal em 2016. Ele é mais conhecido por ser a voz de Kirito do Sword Art Online, Sorata Kanda da Pet Girl of Sakurasou, Sora de No Game No Life, Arata Kasuga / Trinity Astral de Trinity Seven, Sōma Yukihira de Food Wars !: Shokugeki no Soma e Masamune Izumi de Eromanga Sensei. Em 17 de junho de 2019, ele é o atual detentor oficial do Guinness World Record das mordidas de som mais exclusivas fornecidas por um dublador com mais de 10.000 palavras em Danmachi - Memoria Freese.","name":"Yoshitsugu Matsuoka","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"","name":"Yoshitsugu Matsuoka","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"松岡禎丞是日本的男性聲優。出身於北海道帶廣市，所屬公司為 I'm Enterprise。","name":"松岡禎丞","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"마츠오카 요시츠구","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","english_name":"Thai","data":{"biography":"","name":"โยชิตสึงุ มัตสึโอกะ","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"Yoshitsugu Matsuoka","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Ёсицугу Мацуока","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CZ","iso_639_1":"cs","name":"Český","english_name":"Czech","data":{"biography":"","name":"Jošicugu Macuoka","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IT","iso_639_1":"it","name":"Italiano","english_name":"Italian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Yoshitsugu Matsuoka","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"PT","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Yoshitsugu Matsuoka","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"Йошіцуґу Мацуока — японський актор озвучування з Хоккайдо. Він пов’язаний з I'm Enterprise.\n\nЙого було відзначено на 6-й церемонії вручення премії «Сейю» за найкращого нового актора в 2012 році та на 10-й церемонії вручення премії «Сейю» за найкращу чоловічу роль у 2016 році.\n\nСтаном на 17 червня 2019 року він є поточним офіційним рекордсменом Книги рекордів Гіннеса за найбільш унікальними звуковими фрагментами, озвученими актором із понад 10 000 слів у Danmachi - Memoria Freese.","name":"Йошіцуґу Мацуока","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"EE","iso_639_1":"ee","name":"Èʋegbe","english_name":"Ewe","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"松岡禎丞是日本的男性聲優。出身於北海道帶廣市，所屬公司為 I'm Enterprise。","name":"松岡禎丞","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"SA","iso_639_1":"ar","name":"العربية","english_name":"Arabic","data":{"biography":"","name":"يوشيتسوغو ماتسوؤكا","primary":false}}]}},"movie_1238188_keywords":{"at":1772691634787,"data":{"id":1238188,"keywords":[{"id":158718,"name":"lgbt"},{"id":258533,"name":"gay theme"}]}},"person_5922611_translations":{"at":1772691639610,"data":{"id":5922611,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Ecaterina Mitroiu","primary":true}}]}},"person_544531_translations":{"at":1772691652235,"data":{"id":544531,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Shaheizy Sam bin Abdul Samad (born 4 September 1982) is a Malaysian actor, singer and producer who was known as a young star in the 1990s before rising to fame in the controversial movie, Bohsia: Jangan Pilih Jalan Hitam in 2009, and the box office movie, Adnan Sempit in the following year.","name":"Shaheizy Sam","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"SG","iso_639_1":"ms","name":"Bahasa melayu","english_name":"Malay","data":{"biography":"","name":"Shaheizy Sam","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"MY","iso_639_1":"ms","name":"Bahasa melayu","english_name":"Malay","data":{"biography":"Shaheizy Sam Abdul Samad ialah seorang pelakon lelaki Malaysia yang menempa nama sebagai pelakon remaja pada era 1990-an. Beliau membuat kemunculan pertamanya dalam bidang lakonan pada 1995 menerusi filem Sama Tak Serupa bersama Aznil Nawawi sebelum melonjak naik dalam bidang perfileman melalui filem kontroversi Bohsia: Jangan Pilih Jalan Hitam (2009) dan filem aksi komedi Adnan Sempit (2010-14). Sam telah berlakon dalam beberapa filem pecah panggung termasuk Jangan Pandang Belakang Congkak (2009), Evolusi KL Drift 2 (2010), Kongsi (2011), Sekali Lagi (2011), Bini-Biniku Gangster (2011), Songlap (2011), SAM: Saya Amat Mencintaimu (2012), Mamak Cupcake (2014), Polis EVO (2015-23), Interchange (2016), Pinjamkan Hatiku (2017) dan MALBATT: Misi Bakara (2023). Selain berlakon filem, Sam telah muncul dalam beberapa drama televisyen seperti Kasanova XXL (2009), Impak Maksima the Series (2009), Adnan Sempit the Series (2010-11), Kisah Cinta (2013), Aku Bukan Bimbo (2016) dan lain-lain lagi. Beliau memulakan kerjaya muziknya pada 1998 dengan menganggotai kumpulan M.O.B sehingga pembubaran mereka.\n\nSepanjang kerjayanya dalam bidang lakonan, Sam telah bekerjasama dengan ramai rakan seangkatannya, termasuk Syamsul Yusof, Farid Kamil, Lisa Surihani, Yana Samsudin dan Intan Ladyana. Beliau telah menerima pelbagai anugerah dan pencalonan dalam televisyen, filem dan platform lain, termasuk dua pencalonan bagi Pelakon Pembantu Lelaki Terbaik di Festival Filem Malaysia ke-22 (menerusi Bohsia: Jangan Pilih Jalan Hitam) dan ke-23 (menerusi Evolusi KL Drift 2), serta memenangi Pelakon Lelaki Terbaik di Festival Filem Malaysia ke-24, beliau turut memenangi Bintang Paling Popular di Anugerah Bintang Popular Berita Harian 2014. Anugerah lain yang diraih oleh beliau termasuk Anugerah Shout!, Anugerah Skrin, Anugerah Blokbuster, Anugerah Pilihan Pembaca Media Hiburan dan Anugerah Lawak Warna. Pada Jun 2018, Harian Metro menyenaraikan beliau sebagai salah seorang dari 10 pelakon popular yang meraih pengiktirafan di peringkat global.","name":"Shaheizy Sam","primary":true}}]}},"person_3116034_translations":{"at":1772691656667,"data":{"id":3116034,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"A rising South Korean actor and model belonging to the Namyang Hong clan. He is currently a student in the Acting Department at the Seoul Institute of the Arts and is managed by Fable Company. In 2019, he appeared in the Dingo Studio dating web variety show Lookating. He made his official acting debut in 2020 through the web drama 187cm 155cm and subsequently starred in several web series. In 2024, he made his first television appearance in the tvN drama Love on a Single Log Bridge. His notable works include The Love-Struck Thief and Study Group.","name":"Hong Min-gi","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"대한민국의 신예 배우이자 모델로, 본관은 남양 홍씨이다. 현재 서울예술대학교 연기과에 재학 중이며, 소속사는 페이블컴퍼니(Fable Company)이다. 2019년 딩고 스튜디오(Dingo Studio)의 소개팅 웹 예능 ‘루카팅(Lookating)’에 출연했다. 2020년 웹드라마 ‘187cm 155cm’를 통해 배우로 정식 데뷔한 후 다수의 웹드라마에 출연했다. 2024년 tvN 드라마 ‘사랑은 외나무다리에서’에 출연하며 TV 드라마 신고식을 치렀다. 주요 출연작으로는 ‘은애하는 도적님’, ‘스터디그룹’ 등이 있다.","name":"홍민기","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"韩国新生代演员、模特，本贯南阳洪氏， 首尔艺术大学表演系在读，隶属于Fable Company。2019年，参加Dingo Studio推出的相亲网综《Lookating》。2020年，通过网剧《187cm 155cm》作为演员正式出道，随后拍摄多部网剧。2024年，参演tvN《爱在独木桥》建立知名度。代表作包括《恩爱的盗贼大人》、《流氓读书会》等。","name":"洪民基","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Hong Min Ki","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"韓國新生代演員、模特兒，本貫南陽洪氏，現就讀於首爾藝術大學表演系，隸屬於 Fable Company。2019 年，參加 Dingo Studio 推出的相親網綜《Lookating》。2020 年，透過網劇《187cm 155cm》作為演員正式出道，隨後拍攝多部網劇。2024 年，參演 tvN《愛在獨木橋》，首次在電視劇（無線/有線台）中亮相。代表作包括《恩愛的盜賊大人》、《流氓讀書會》等。","name":"洪民基","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"韓國新生代演員、模特兒，本貫南陽洪氏，現就讀於首爾藝術大學表演系，隸屬於 Fable Company。2019年，參加 Dingo Studio 推出的相親網綜《Lookating》。2020年，透過網劇《187cm 155cm》作為演員正式出道，隨後拍攝多部網劇。2024年，參演 tvN《愛在獨木橋》，首次在電視劇（無線/有線台）中亮相。代表作包括《恩愛的盜賊大人》、《流氓讀書會》等。","name":"洪民基","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"SK","iso_639_1":"sk","name":"Slovenčina","english_name":"Slovak","data":{"biography":"","name":"Hong Min-gi","primary":false}}]}},"person_1343551_translations":{"at":1772691667895,"data":{"id":1343551,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Aom Phiyada Akkaraseranee is a Thai actress, model, and host. She is the second daughter of Pisarn Akarasenee, a well-known actor and producer of various popular Thai TV series.\n\nPhiyada Akkraseranee graduated with a Bachelor of Science degree in education from the Srinakharinwirot University in Bangkok. She began her career as a model for commercials on TV in 1996. Her first drama as the leading actress was \"Torfun and Marwin\" produced by Exact co.\n\nAom gained a lot of popular and talent Awards including Best Actress in Asian Television Awards. Meanwhile, Aom also became a hot host of variety talk shows for Wan Warn Yang Wharn You and E-mouth in 2004.\n\nAom married Art Sara Jutharattanakul in August 2009, and their wedding reception was held in October 2009. They have a daughter named Nava.","name":"Phiyada Jutharattanakul","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","english_name":"Thai","data":{"biography":"","name":"พิยดา จุฑารัตนกุล","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"拼塔安·阿孔萨妮","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"拼塔安·阿孔薩妮","primary":false}}]}}}}